Suggests: ${phpcomposer:Debian-suggest}
Description: OpenVPN client connection manager
 The package provides a simple PHP library managing client connections to
 OpenVPN processes through the OpenVPN management socket.  It features:
 - Traversing multiple OpenVPN management sockets;
 - Show connected clients;
 - Disconnect clients (by CN).
